## 12. Conclusion

The Search Algorithm Analyzer successfully demonstrates the differences between various search algorithms. It highlights how different strategies lead to different results in terms of cost and efficiency. Among all, A* algorithm performs best in most cases due to its balanced approach using cost and heuristic.

This project provides a strong foundation for understanding artificial intelligence search techniques.

